    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a fair point about the vetoes. but do historians think the UN is actually still a legitimate way to handle global security, or is the whole idea of international cooperation basically seen as a failed experiment by now? like, is there even a real debate about its legitimacy anymore?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
